==Demographics==
{| class="toccolours" align="right" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 1em 1em; font-size: 95%;"
|-
! colspan="3" bgcolor="#ccccff" align="center"| '''City of Providence<br>Population by year<ref name=population/><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.census.gov/population/documentation/twps0027/tab01.txt | title=Rank by Population of the 100 Largest Urban Places, Listed Alphabetically by State: 1790-1990 | date=[[January 12]] [[2007]] | publisher=U.S. Census Bureau | accessdate = 2007-01-17}}</ref><ref name=population>{{cite web | author=Gibson, Campbell | date=June 1998 | url=http://www.census.gov/population/www/documentation/twps0027.html |title=Population of the 100 Largest Cities and Other Urban Places in the United States: 1790 to 1990 | publisher=U.S. Census Bureau - Population Division | accessdate = 2007-01-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.city-data.com/us-cities/The-Northeast/Providence.html | title=Providence| publisher=U.S. Census Bureau | year=[[June 20]] [[2006]] | accessdate = 2007-01-17}}</ref>'''
